{"id":14805,"date":"2021-10-07T14:53:41","date_gmt":"2021-10-07T07:53:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/?p=14805"},"modified":"2021-10-07T15:04:16","modified_gmt":"2021-10-07T08:04:16","slug":"loi-ich-cua-dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-ich-cua-dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep.html\/","title":{"rendered":"L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_36 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">N\u1ed9i Dung<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" style=\"display: none;\"><label for=\"item\" aria-label=\"Table of Content\"><span style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;width: 35px;height: 30px;justify-content: center;\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"item\"><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-ich-cua-dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#Y_nghia_cua_PR_va_tai_sao_phai_viet_bai_PR\" title=\"\u00dd ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a PR v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i sao ph\u1ea3i vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR?\u00a0\">\u00dd ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a PR v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i sao ph\u1ea3i vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR?\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-ich-cua-dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#Loi_ich_cua_dich_vu_viet_bai_PR\" title=\"L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR\">L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-ich-cua-dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#Tiep_can_dung_doi_tuong_muc_tieu\" title=\"Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau\">Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-ich-cua-dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#Truyen_tai_thong_diep_chinh_xac\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c\">Truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-ich-cua-dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#Su_dung_ngon_tu_chuan_muc_va_linh_hoat\" title=\"S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c v\u00e0 linh ho\u1ea1t\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c v\u00e0 linh ho\u1ea1t<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/loi-ich-cua-dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep.html\/#Dam_bao_ve_hinh_thuc_trinh_bay\" title=\"\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em>PR th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean c\u00e1c trang b\u00e1o \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp, t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nh\u00f3m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tinh t\u1ebf h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i dung b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0<strong>d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong> t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 <strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media<\/strong> l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn uy t\u00edn cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Y_nghia_cua_PR_va_tai_sao_phai_viet_bai_PR\"><\/span><strong>\u00dd ngh\u0129a c\u1ee7a PR v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i sao ph\u1ea3i vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR?\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14820 \" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"943\" height=\"626\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep.png 750w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 943px) 100vw, 943px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>PR (Public Relations) \u2013 quan h\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng ch\u00fang l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, lan t\u1ecfa gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb m\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u mu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, PR th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn, quan \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t b\u00ean th\u1ee9 3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o, chuy\u00ean gia, nh\u00e0 ph\u00ea b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1, nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u00e1ch quan.<\/p>\n<p>Trong PR th\u00ec n\u1ed9i dung PR c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng. B\u00e0i PR s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1ng ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 k\u00edch th\u00edch kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 h\u01a1n. \u1ede m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e0i PR th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng tinh t\u1ebf h\u01a1n, kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o h\u01a1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc \u2013 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.<\/p>\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi vi\u1ebft n\u1ed9i dung PR, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 g\u00ec: B\u00e0i PR th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, b\u00e0i PR s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, b\u00e0i PR d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, PR \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u hay \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng? T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u1ed9i dung cho b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu t\u1ef1 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i, l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi l\u1ed1i vi\u1ebft ch\u1ee7 quan thi\u1ebfu thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a PR. B\u1edfi v\u1eady d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5\u00a0<strong>nh\u1eadn vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR<\/strong>\u00a0l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Loi_ich_cua_dich_vu_viet_bai_PR\"><\/span><strong>L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14819 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep4.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep4-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep4-1024x538.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep4-768x403.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tiep_can_dung_doi_tuong_muc_tieu\"><\/span>Ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1ed7i b\u00e0i PR \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c nhau. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, bao g\u1ed3m th\u00f3i quen, h\u00e0nh vi, nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd quan t\u00e2m, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd mong mu\u1ed1n\u2026T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed7i b\u00e0i PR s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c h\u00fat v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c cao.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Truyen_tai_thong_diep_chinh_xac\"><\/span><span id=\"Truyen_tai_thong_diep_chinh_xac\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span>Truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i PR. Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p n\u00e0y xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh? Th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p trong\u00a0<strong>c\u00e1c b\u00e0i PR<\/strong>\u00a0th\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00eau l\u00ean m\u1ed9t quan \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5, th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m r\u00f5 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00f2n m\u01a1 h\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn, gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean content chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p \u1ea5y m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed7i b\u00e0i PR \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i \u1edf nh\u1eefng n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c nhau, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c nhau. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, bao g\u1ed3m th\u00f3i quen, h\u00e0nh vi, nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd quan t\u00e2m, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd mong mu\u1ed1n\u2026T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 m\u1ed7i b\u00e0i PR s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ee9c h\u00fat v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ednh thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c cao.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Su_dung_ngon_tu_chuan_muc_va_linh_hoat\"><\/span>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c v\u00e0 linh ho\u1ea1t<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i PR l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb, b\u1edfi b\u00e0i PR th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng tr\u00ean b\u00e1o ch\u00ed, trang tin t\u1ee9c \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i hay website b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng.\u00a0<strong>D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR<\/strong>\u00a0chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c, s\u00fac t\u00edch v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch quan. Tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh linh ho\u1ea1t t\u00f9y theo \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dam_bao_ve_hinh_thuc_trinh_bay\"><\/span>\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>M\u1ed9t b\u00e0i PR th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac r\u00e0nh m\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng video, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh minh h\u1ecda \u0111\u1eb9p. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea7n ng\u00f4n t\u1eeb,\u00a0<strong>d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong>\u00a0s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft theo b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y n\u1ed9i dung minh h\u1ecda m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u1edf n\u00ean sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady \u2013 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong PR.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14821 \" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"943\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep1.jpg 800w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep1-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/dich-vu-viet-bai-pr-chuyen-nghiep1-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 943px) 100vw, 943px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn\u00a0<strong>b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR<\/strong> tr\u00ean b\u00e1o ch\u00ed v\u00e0 c\u00e1c trang tin t\u1ee9c \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng. \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2y vi\u1ebft gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i PR hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft PR unique 100%, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o mang \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed9i dung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/li>\n<li>Th\u1eddi gian vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/li>\n<li>Chi ph\u00ed h\u1ee3p l\u00fd cho m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng cao gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u v\u00e0 uy t\u00edn tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>PR th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u tr\u00ean c\u00e1c trang b\u00e1o \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp, t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn nh\u00f3m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tinh t\u1ebf h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i dung b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng tr\u1ef1c di\u1ec7n. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng\u00a0d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":14819,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[74,59,73,87,79,51,78,77],"tags":[890,889,881,891,892],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>L\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p - \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media Digital Marketing<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"D\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR uy t\u00edn, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i PR cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/achaume